2014;;If You Love Your Children;;Canadian;;Sanjay Patel;;Akash Sinha, Neha Kaul;;short;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/If_You_Love_Your_Children;;If You Love Your Children is a story of Raj, an engineer working in the energy industry who wants to write a book about climate change. In his quest to get the book published, he loses everything - his job, his girl and his hope. But Raj finds his commitment to be stronger than his desires and in the end, he rises above his losses to realize his dream.